This isn't spectacular, but it is a simple tasty recipe that is made with ingredients I usually have on hand. I added some black beans and chicken to make it a little more substantial. Also, I grilled my quesidillas on a George Foreman grill. Worked great...toasted both sides (no need for flipping).

